1. *Obzirom* da je protok vremena neumitno, moramo biti najefikasniji. (Given that the flow of time is inevitable, we must be most efficient.) 
2. Svi razgovori su bili obustavljeni *obzirom* na stanje u zemlji. (All talks were suspended considering the state of the country.) 
3. *Obzirom* na to da je jedan od sudionika odsutan, sastanak je odgođen. (Given that one of the participants is absent, the meeting was postponed.) 
4. *Obzirom* da je nivo aktivnosti vrlo visok, moramo biti pažljivi. (Considering the level of activity is very high, we must be careful.)